snippet.title: Marshmellow Spa Day - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
https://lesser-panda.itch.io/marshmellow-day-spa

Made in 3 days for Winter Jam. Become a marshmallow with one mission: making the perfect hot cocoa bath for other marshmallows who seek a relaxed escape from the busy marshmallow life.
